title: Perilous Crystal Caves Website...
content:
Well, a select few PCKFers already know about the Crystal Caves website Ive been working on for some time now (quite some time...but thats another story...). Ive finally finished what I had planned for it; so, heres a link. Click if you dare:

[url=http://txv.shortcutman.net/pccw/]Perilous Crystal Caves Website[/url]
(its a Crystal Caves website, if you hadnt guessed from the title)


Its got a decent amount of content (in my opinion, anyway), but if anyone can spot a gaping hole, content wise, let me know whats missing and Ill do my best to correct/ add straight away.

Something Id be quite interested to hear feedback on is the information in the trivia sections; these sections werent derived from any Crystal Caves sources (well, most werent) so I dont know how accurate these are in relation to Crystal Caves.

So, have a poke around and let me know what you think and/or any problems you encounter, and, as the clich goes:

[clich] dont forget to sign the guestbook! [/clich]
